rows.label: qst100303_msg0001
rows.name:
[ML:Feeling kind=Anger ]I'm not going to be food
in a place like this, mo!

rows.label: qst100303_msg0002
rows.name:
Pupun has a dream, mo! To eat all
the delicious food in Alst...

rows.label: qst100303_msg0003
rows.name:
Ugh... Those eyes are saying they're
going to eat Pupun up, mo...

rows.label: qst100303_msg0004
rows.name:
Ah! The kind person
who gave Pupun food!

rows.label: qst100303_msg0101
rows.name:
Thank you, mo... I was about to
become a Vacuum Grogg's snack, mo.

rows.label: qst100303_msg0102
rows.name:
...Those eyes are saying you think
Pupun is a heartless Nopon who won't
thank you for the food, mo!

rows.label: qst100303_msg0103
rows.name:
Aah, wait, wait, mo. Don't
say such scary things, mo. I
didn't mean any harm, mo.

rows.label: qst100303_msg0104
rows.name:
When I grab the helm, I tend
to get carried away and
become aggressive, mo...

rows.label: qst100303_msg0105
rows.name:
I'll go to Invidia... and when
I return to Avaritia, I'll
give you your reward, mo.

rows.label: qst100303_msg0106
rows.name:
This time, for sure! Definitely!
It's a definite promise, mo.

rows.label: qst100303_msg0107
rows.name:
[ML:Feeling kind=Anger ]Hahaha! Witness the
skill of Pupun-sama...

rows.label: qst100303_msg0108
rows.name:
Momomo? The helm feels
a bit wobbly, mo...
